Field Detail

PROPERTY_KIND_STRING

static final java.lang.String PROPERTY_KIND_STRING
A property kind for string properties. This is the default property kind.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

PROPERTY_KIND_READONLY_STRING

static final java.lang.String PROPERTY_KIND_READONLY_STRING
A property kind for readonly string properties. The intention is that there is no way in the UI to edit, rename, or delete readonly properties. These properties must be created and manipulated programatically.

Since:
0.6.1

getKind

java.lang.String getKind()
Get the property kind. Property kind is used to find the registered editor for the property. A property kind of empty string or PROPERTY_KIND_STRING will use the default string editing.

Returns:
The property kind.
